data.description: Amazing end unit Townhome! Newer window treatments, furnace, water heater, Fresh Paint ,New Lighting and New Carpet.  This home features an open concept throughout. The main level showcases a large living room with updated  Eat in kitchen area with access to deck and a separate formal dining room area. There are also 2 bedrooms including the large master, with huge walk in closet. The lower level features a family room . There is also a possible 3rd bedroom. The lower level is a walkout. . Close to parks, shopping and entertainment. A must see!!
